group commands is for group management.

Usage:
  boat group <command>

Commands:
  id          Get group by id.
  get         Get group by name.
  list        List groups.
  create      Create new group.
  delete      Delete group by id.
  add         Add host to a group.
  remove      Remove host from group.

Use "boat group <command> -h" for more information about a command.
